{"tid":721793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普: 習近平很棒, 郭台銘很偉大","createTime":"2018-06-29T02:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T08:14:07.000Z","uid":134071,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2f5fba5085d5d60dbf41c10740a338d1fa9b42","tid":721793,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180629/1381860/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1381860%2F&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9609f9c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1381860%2F&h=675c8077\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180629/1381860/</a><br />\n<br />\n鴻海集團在美國威斯康辛州設立的工廠周四舉行動土典禮，美國總統川普和鴻海董事長郭台銘再度同框。郭台銘給足川普面子，現場稱讚他是最有執行力的總統，還說若不是川普當總統，他不會去美國設廠。<br />\n....<br />\n川普致詞時先說郭台銘是他的朋友，並且稱讚他是全球萬中選一的企業家。而除了感謝郭台銘與富士康之外，川普也在談話中批評最近和美國打貿易戰的中國：「<strong>我對中國充滿敬意，我認為中國很好，習近平主席，我認為他很棒</strong>。他也是我的一個朋友。但在過去的幾年的中美貿易裡，我們損失了5000億美元。一年5000億美元。我們重建了中國。總有一天他們會謝謝我們，但我們不想再這樣做了。我們希望有一個在貿易上比較公平和平衡的局面。這種局面未必馬上實現，但至少要公平。」<br />\n <br />\n川普接著說，最近美國最高法院通過的幾項對他有利的判決，其中一項判決會讓郭台銘很高興。川普並沒有點出是哪一項，而只說「你知道的，你知道的」。報導分析，川普指的可能是最高法院本周做出的削弱工會力量的判決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180629/1381792/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1381792%2F&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=87e18108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1381792%2F&h=1a82112b\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180629/1381792/</a><br />\n<br />\n川普今晨為鴻海威州廠動土典禮站台，根據福斯新聞畫面，川普與郭董並肩拿金色鏟子，象徵威州廠正式動土，郭董比出讚的手勢，<strong>川普則拍拍郭董肩膀，並盛讚郭董是世上最偉大商業領袖之一</strong>，還感謝軟銀（SoftBank）執行長孫正義促成鴻海投資美國。川普稍後參觀威州廠現有設施並發表談話，演講時又大讚威州廠是「世界第8大奇蹟」。"},{"pid":"a49f5f0a61b7b346920b25d4936ee843010de63b","tid":721793,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"其實佢面皮真係幾厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05699b3b6fac76933114253d661809d4d12cca2e","tid":721793,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49f5f0a61b7b346920b25d4936ee843010de63b","tid":721793,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"其實佢面皮真係幾厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0408421ad40ec27105f749c67c4b9e0d31cee442","tid":721793,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"下 攞錯左 謊言豆沙包"},{"pid":"0f344401b76c782b57053f9a9ea8f4212a5afd12","tid":721793,"uid":11895,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"其實佢屈到啲廠返美國做都幾好野"},{"pid":"6e25e013878fe047312711a1b5ecb761a156bd38","tid":721793,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"my friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7491d0a2b9bdd4026ba61d1c3113872f46fb04d","tid":721793,"uid":34602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"同中國夢即係美國夢有異曲同功之妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4331cab9533620c2714b88cb4ab9b35d067ea3d","tid":721793,"uid":20815,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"05699b3b6fac76933114253d661809d4d12cca2e","tid":721793,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49f5f0a61b7b346920b25d4936ee843010de63b","tid":721793,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"其實佢面皮真係幾厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo